egory\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":665,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/31\/sweetness-faith-contentment\/","url_meta":{"origin":263,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Sweetness of faith is satisfaction with Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-'Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe has tasted the sweetness of faith who is content with Allah as a Lord, Islam as a religion, and Muhammad as a messenger.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 34 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/believer-or-merely-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":263,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Or maybe he is merely a Muslim?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was distributing charity, so I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, give it to this man for he is a believer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOr merely a Muslim.\u201d I said it three times and the Prophet repeated it three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1720,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/04\/ghurabah-islam-began-strange\/","url_meta":{"origin":263,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ghuraba: Islam began as strange, blessed are strangers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 4, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cIslam began as something strange and it will return to being strange, so blessed are the strangers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u00a0145 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0628\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0623\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":359,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/08\/priorities-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":263,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dawah: Priorities of Islam are faith, prayer, charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent me to Yemen\u00a0and he said, \u201cVerily, you are going to people among the people of the Book, so 